On freelancer's marketplaces, where people sell any kind of services for a very varied range of prices, 
        you can find a lot of offers for cheap content promotion.
        In the following photos, for example, we can see hundreds of gig workers on Fiverr (a famous freelancer marketplace) 
        which sell services targeted at musicians willing to boost their popularity on social media.

title: Fiverr - "I will promote your spotify music and make it viral"
